{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm here because I have a very important message:"},{"time":3000,"text":"I think we have found"},{"time":5000,"text":"the most important factor for success."},{"time":8000,"text":"And it was found close to here, Stanford."},{"time":13000,"text":"Psychology professor took kids that were four years old"},{"time":17000,"text":"and put them in a room all by themselves."},{"time":21000,"text":"And he would tell the child, a four-year-old kid,"},{"time":24000,"text":"\"Johnny, I am going to leave you here with a marshmallow"},{"time":27000,"text":"for 15 minutes."},{"time":29000,"text":"If, after I come back, this marshmallow is here,"},{"time":33000,"text":"you will get another one. So you will have two.\""},{"time":37000,"text":"To tell a four-year-old kid to wait 15 minutes"},{"time":40000,"text":"for something that they like,"},{"time":42000,"text":"is equivalent to telling us, \"We'll bring you coffee in two hours.\""},{"time":46000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":47000,"text":"Exact equivalent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49000,"text":"So what happened when the professor left the room?"},{"time":54000,"text":"As soon as the door closed..."},{"time":58000,"text":"two out of three ate the marshmallow."},{"time":60000,"text":"Five seconds, 10 seconds, 40 seconds, 50 seconds,"},{"time":63000,"text":"two minutes, four minutes, eight minutes."},{"time":65000,"text":"Some lasted 14-and-a-half minutes."},{"time":68000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":69000,"text":"Couldn't do it. Could not wait."},{"time":73000,"text":"What's interesting is that one out of three"},{"time":76000,"text":"would look at the marshmallow and go like this ..."},{"time":81000,"text":"Would look at it."},{"time":83000,"text":"Put it back."},{"time":85000,"text":"They would walk around. They would play with their skirts and pants."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"That child already, at four, understood"},{"time":93000,"text":"the most important principle for success,"},{"time":96000,"text":"which is the ability to delay gratification."},{"time":100000,"text":"Self-discipline:"},{"time":102000,"text":"the most important factor for success."},{"time":105000,"text":"15 years later, 14 or 15 years later,"},{"time":108000,"text":"follow-up study."},{"time":110000,"text":"What did they find?"},{"time":112000,"text":"They went to look for these kids who were now 18 and 19."},{"time":115000,"text":"And they found that 100 percent"},{"time":118000,"text":"of the children that had not eaten the marshmallow were successful."},{"time":122000,"text":"They had good grades. They were doing wonderful."},{"time":124000,"text":"They were happy. They had their plans."},{"time":126000,"text":"They had good relationships with the teachers, students."},{"time":129000,"text":"They were doing fine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130000,"text":"A great percentage of the kids that ate the marshmallow,"},{"time":133000,"text":"they were in trouble."},{"time":134000,"text":"They did not make it to university."},{"time":136000,"text":"They had bad grades. Some of them dropped out."},{"time":138000,"text":"A few were still there with bad grades."},{"time":140000,"text":"A few had good grades."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"I had a question in my mind: Would Hispanic kids"},{"time":144000,"text":"react the same way as the American kids?"},{"time":147000,"text":"So I went to Colombia. And I reproduced the experiment."},{"time":150000,"text":"And it was very funny. I used four, five and six years old kids."},{"time":153000,"text":"And let me show you what happened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171000,"text":"(Spanish) (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":272000,"text":"So what happened in Colombia?"},{"time":274000,"text":"Hispanic kids, two out of three ate the marshmallow;"},{"time":277000,"text":"one out of three did not."},{"time":279000,"text":"This little girl was interesting;"},{"time":281000,"text":"she ate the inside of the marshmallow."},{"time":283000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":284000,"text":"In other words, she wanted us to think that she had not eaten it, so she would get two."},{"time":288000,"text":"But she ate it."},{"time":290000,"text":"So we know she'll be successful. But we have to watch her."},{"time":293000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":294000,"text":"She should not go into banking, for example,"},{"time":297000,"text":"or work at a cash register."},{"time":299000,"text":"But she will be successful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301000,"text":"And this applies for everything. Even in sales."},{"time":303000,"text":"The sales person that --"},{"time":307000,"text":"the customer says, \"I want that.\" And the person says, \"Okay, here you are.\""},{"time":309000,"text":"That person ate the marshmallow."},{"time":311000,"text":"If the sales person says, \"Wait a second."},{"time":313000,"text":"Let me ask you a few questions to see if this is a good choice.\""},{"time":316000,"text":"Then you sell a lot more."},{"time":317000,"text":"So this has applications in all walks of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322000,"text":"I end with -- the Koreans did this."},{"time":325000,"text":"You know what? This is so good"},{"time":327000,"text":"that we want a marshmallow book for children."},{"time":329000,"text":"We did one for children. And now it is all over Korea."},{"time":332000,"text":"They are teaching these kids exactly this principle."},{"time":334000,"text":"And we need to learn that principle here in the States,"},{"time":336000,"text":"because we have a big debt."},{"time":338000,"text":"We are eating more marshmallows than we are producing."},{"time":340000,"text":"Thank you so much."}]}]}